{"tid":2115014,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母點解要醫護埋單呀","createTime":"2020-07-19T08:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T17:15:36.000Z","uid":53096,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f22535072dd144d31441d73da75489732744d343","tid":2115014,"uid":53096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路睇4點鐘7婆個閪樣一路諗<br />\n點解當初我地叫你封關你唔封<br />\n諗無可諗罷工叫你封你都唔封<br />\n你老母臭閪仲話要抽後算帳<br />\n仆你個街依家奶撚晒野<br />\n啲公務員可以home office<br />\n我地就E Level開始返足咁多日<br />\n逼我地SHS幫人探熱守門口<br />\n人工又唔撚加,今年已經要凍薪<br />\n依家你有面叫人共渡時艱?<br />\n點解可以咁撚唔公平<br />\n點解要當醫護係condom<br />\n點解政府可以咁撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry 有感而發..<br />\n見到其他醫院已經確診<br />\n而聽日自己又要上路<br />\n每日放工都好驚中左會傳比屋企人<br />\n你班撚樣高官日日嘆冷氣<br />\n難為我地大熱天著晒full gear<br />\n日日要擋住班唔戴口罩廢老<br />\n死就我地死先,你就日日係電視前面9up<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc514b492ef461080e9a9173c3002e0eff9a0ba2","tid":2115014,"uid":54721,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"因為自己停左罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34b93f04b6629dd72926f244e8a2428d1ff9199","tid":2115014,"uid":53096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲屋企人依家仲成日話好難搵工<br />\n叫我比心機做....屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3257ee26e6d0b55ad74b3b39f0c6507420bdab48","tid":2115014,"uid":88725,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"你地自己投降係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d4539709b694cd0d95a6adaeae839de6c535d5","tid":2115014,"uid":294648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"知錯能改